# Frontend build-time config (optional).
# For a single-service deploy (Express serves the built app + API), leave this
# unset — the app calls the API at the same origin under /api.
# For a SPLIT deploy (static frontend + separate API host), set this to the
# full API base URL, e.g. https://api.yourdomain.com/api
# VITE_API_URL=/api
